                                + "while processing payment " + paymentId
                );
            }
        }

        // ── SUCCESS PATH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
        String providerTxnRef = "PROVB-" + UUID.randomUUID().toString().replace("-", "").substring(0, 16).toUpperCase();
        log.info("[{}] Successfully processed payment [{}]. Provider reference: {}",
